order of options in component:
name
inheritAttrs
data
props
computed
components
methods
created
mounted

known bugs / issues:
- this is an issue with Vue 2 (will be fixed in Vue 3). `class` and `style`
  attributes cannot be (reliably) passed with `v-bind='$attrs'`. for now, the
  code has separate attributes for these: `mclass` and `mstyle`.
  todo: replace these in Vue 3 accordingly.
